79b2c2ce-27f1-485f-a661-cda9186dd0b4.title: Note
79b2c2ce-27f1-485f-a661-cda9186dd0b4.text:
this guy is in 2 locations and has differing dialogue for each, 
though not by much.. mayeb
 gotta do quest stikll

75540054-4402-4137-9776-b8e51225d920.title: Note
75540054-4402-4137-9776-b8e51225d920.text: quick follow interactions, lets for fast teleport

43f4e16a-07fd-45e4-95f8-dd4ecd7dd1c6.title: Elkoy
43f4e16a-07fd-45e4-95f8-dd4ecd7dd1c6.text: Hello, welcome to our village. I'm Elkoy the tree gnome.

de7f167e-eccc-4960-adf4-366f95708e71.title: <player>
de7f167e-eccc-4960-adf4-366f95708e71.text: I haven't heard of your sort before.

100921c9-94a1-4c45-b4c8-c2eed2c39850.title: Elkoy
100921c9-94a1-4c45-b4c8-c2eed2c39850.text:
There's not many of us left. Once you could find tree
gnomes anywhere in the world, now we hide in small
groups to avoid capture.

11320966-8048-4574-abab-7110b83f72cc.title: Elkoy
11320966-8048-4574-abab-7110b83f72cc.text:
Tree gnomes have been hunted for so called 'fun' since
as long as I can remember.

9f8bf4b2-c3a5-48e4-b545-e9cc9d8f92f8.title: Elkoy
9f8bf4b2-c3a5-48e4-b545-e9cc9d8f92f8.text:
Our main threat nowadays are General Khazard's
troops. They know no mercy, but are also very dense.
They'll never find their way through our maze.

e1782bde-ff7c-4c41-b0fc-37a156436d2e.title: Note
e1782bde-ff7c-4c41-b0fc-37a156436d2e.text:
TELEPORTS YOU TO THE ENTRANCE OF
THE MAZE, NORTHWESTERN ENTRANCE

9a389aea-621c-4435-8c77-f616e8e38c13.title: Elkoy
9a389aea-621c-4435-8c77-f616e8e38c13.text:
The orb, they have the orb. We're doomed.
Do you need me to show you through the maze?

98b7aba0-f86e-4155-9cd5-1ede17028594.text: Elkoy guides you through the maze.

30f56412-1f67-4d13-bee6-e9618f11fcb8.title: Elkoy
30f56412-1f67-4d13-bee6-e9618f11fcb8.text: Please help us get our orb back.

5a903d03-1640-4a8e-88ef-795881becd11.title: Elkoy
5a903d03-1640-4a8e-88ef-795881becd11.text:
You must retrieve the orb, or the gnome village is
doomed. Do you need me to show you through the
maze?

e7d39f19-6ec5-4c97-9150-02d732458566.text: Elkoy guides you through the maze.

c28e107f-ebb4-476e-9c3f-c705fb19eb08.title: Elkoy
c28e107f-ebb4-476e-9c3f-c705fb19eb08.text: Please help us get our orb back.

1c7ac3dd-5710-471f-8016-1076a0470f50.text: Elkoy guides you through the maze.

dd8faf8d-d7db-43cd-a7f0-5b07b6669e70.title: Elkoy
dd8faf8d-d7db-43cd-a7f0-5b07b6669e70.text: Please return with our orb soon.

6c74dbb4-dd13-44bd-815e-b83ebafc2601.title: <player>
6c74dbb4-dd13-44bd-815e-b83ebafc2601.text: Hello Elkoy. I have the orb.

80971f87-a098-4eac-8dfb-af85ff2853f9.title: Elkoy
80971f87-a098-4eac-8dfb-af85ff2853f9.text:
Take it to King Bolren, I'm sure he'll be pleased to see
you.

options.text: Can you show me out of the village?

debea7ad-be08-49fe-a86e-29f86d290aff.title: Untitled
debea7ad-be08-49fe-a86e-29f86d290aff.text: Can you show me out of the village?

6abbd39d-c203-40b1-8f9c-499e4793a2e5.title: Elkoy
6abbd39d-c203-40b1-8f9c-499e4793a2e5.text:
Please, we must have the orb if we are to survive.
Do you need me to show you through the maze?

f4ea63b5-e229-4cd6-9ee4-8eb3ef9909b2.text: Elkoy guides you through the maze.

16d4eb4c-e85b-45e3-ab93-428452233842.title: Elkoy
16d4eb4c-e85b-45e3-ab93-428452233842.text: Please help us get our orb back.

027ed9c6-0c06-4c6d-9561-e30ab6ce5c93.title: Note
027ed9c6-0c06-4c6d-9561-e30ab6ce5c93.text:
TELEPORTS YOU TO THE ENTRANCE OF
THE MAZE, NORTHWESTERN ENTRANCE

8b7745cf-b44a-4360-ae67-a5ee2082638e.text: Elkoy guides you through the maze.

8570144c-481d-4df7-8806-3703822b766f.title: Elkoy
8570144c-481d-4df7-8806-3703822b766f.text: Please help us find the orbs.

48dd4e72-5d11-4376-a2b6-2cde8f0fa97f.title: Elkoy
48dd4e72-5d11-4376-a2b6-2cde8f0fa97f.text:
Khazard's men have pillaged the village! They
slaughtered many, and took the other orbs in an
attempt to lead us out of the maze. When will the
misery end?

options.text: Can you show me out of the village?

75a48085-362c-439b-88a0-df654ac4b31d.title: <player>
75a48085-362c-439b-88a0-df654ac4b31d.text: Can you show me out of the village?

dffa405d-5f8d-4d9d-ab14-35e454f27d99.title: Note
dffa405d-5f8d-4d9d-ab14-35e454f27d99.text:
TELEPORTS YOU TO THE ENTRANCE OF
THE MAZE, NORTHWESTERN ENTRANCE

baef9e06-a2c3-43db-a45a-09cf64767259.text: Elkoy guides you through the maze.

14ccfd7f-da2c-4449-ab20-8edec9e6cf9c.title: Elkoy
14ccfd7f-da2c-4449-ab20-8edec9e6cf9c.text: Here we are. Have a safe journey.

44f4cf17-9924-410a-9654-30109b9282f9.title: Elkoy
44f4cf17-9924-410a-9654-30109b9282f9.text:
You saved us by returning the orbs of protection. I'm
humbled and wish you well. Would you like me to show
you through the maze?

abe826ef-d776-4e91-968b-23b9b45f49f2.title: Elkoy
abe826ef-d776-4e91-968b-23b9b45f49f2.text:
Hi there, I hope life is treating you well. Would you
like me to show you the way out of the village?

7ec1d472-b11c-4763-8aa7-1c62cc183122.text: Elkoy guides you through the maze.

a0a530c0-69e0-48ef-9e80-9eb4b1227c36.title: Elkoy
a0a530c0-69e0-48ef-9e80-9eb4b1227c36.text: Here we are. Have a safe journey.
